Package branch

Class OrderManagement

java.lang.Object
branch.OrderManagement
public class OrderManagement extends Object
  • Facilitates the manipulation of any customers orders in the branch
  • This is different from "ItemManagement", where item management focused on all food items within the branch
  • This class focuses on all orders made by customers within the branch, which also contain all food item along with their respective quantities
    • Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    FDAB 2

      • Adds a order to the branch
